 *  A BSC deflationary token with LOTTERY and Marketing support.
 *  
 *  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 *  
 * 
 *  Total Supply            1,000,000,000,000
 *  Minimum Hold                    1,000,000
 *  Winning Amount              1,000,000,000
 *  Max Transaction            10,000,000,000
 * 
 *  At each transaction:
 *  - %2 is burnt
 *  - %5 is goes to lottery pool
 *  - %3 is  goes to Marketing wallet
 *  
 *  Set slippage to         11% - 15%
 *
